source: TEXT_BANSAH107_01385_SEQ_00<tab>Fyuu seeks your aid in broadening the culinary horizons of his spawnbrothers.
target: TEXT_BANSAH107_01385_SEQ_00<tab>Fyuu cherche à varier le menu servi à ses petits frères.

source: TEXT_BANSAH107_01385_SEQ_01<tab>Concerned that his younger siblings' diet has been restricted to what can be caught in the waters near the nursery, Fyuu requests that you procure some ocean delicacies from somewhat further afield. Borrow an elbst from Pahh to cross the waves, and collect the whitecap clams found on the beach of Moonshade Isle.
target: TEXT_BANSAH107_01385_SEQ_01<tab>Fyuu veut s'assurer que ses petits frères bénéficient d'une ali<var 16 /var>men<var 16 /var>ta<var 16 /var>tion variée. Il aimerait donc que vous alliez chercher cinq <var 33 ((EventItem)) 0DF61E89750302 /var> sur l'îlet d'Ombrelune. Vous pouvez vous y rendre en chevauchant un des elbsts de Pahh.

source: TEXT_BANSAH107_01385_SEQ_02<tab>You have gathered an armful of whitecap clams. Return to Novv's Nursery and deliver your haul to Fyuu.
target: TEXT_BANSAH107_01385_SEQ_02<tab>Vous avez obtenu cinq <var 33 ((EventItem)) 0DF61E89750302 /var>. Allez les livrer à Fyuu à la Couvée de Novv.

source: TEXT_BANSAH107_01385_SEQ_03<tab>Fyuu's eyes appear to bulge even further from his head when he beholds the bounty with which you have returned. Judging by his joyful reaction, it may not be long before you find yourself back on an elbst, headed for the sands of Moonshade Isle once more...
target: TEXT_BANSAH107_01385_SEQ_03<tab>Fyuu n'a pas caché sa sa<var 16 /var>tis<var 16 /var>fac<var 16 /var>tion à la vue des délicieux clams que vous lui avez rapportés. À en juger par sa réaction, vous retournerez pro<var 16 /var>ba<var 16 /var>ble<var 16 /var>ment à l'îlet d'Ombrelune en quête de nourriture dans un avenir pas si lointain...

source: TEXT_BANSAH107_01385_TODO_00<tab>Gather whitecap clams on Moonshade Isle.
TEXT_BANSAH107_01385_TODO_01<tab>Deliver the whitecap clams to Fyuu.
target: TEXT_BANSAH107_01385_TODO_01<tab>Livrer les <var 33 ((EventItem)) 0DF61E89750302 /var> à Fyuu à la Couvée de Novv

source: TEXT_BANSAH107_01385_FYUU_000_000<tab>Pshhh... There are many duties that occupy my time here in the nursssery, not the leassst of which is keeping the hatchlings fed.
target: TEXT_BANSAH107_01385_FYUU_000_000<tab>Fsshhh, nous avons de nombreuses tâches dans la Couvée, et nourrir les alevins n'est pas la moindre.

source: TEXT_BANSAH107_01385_FYUU_000_001<tab>And though there are many fishhh to be had in the nearby waters, it would be nice to expose my little ssspawnbrothers to more of what the sssea has to offer.
target: TEXT_BANSAH107_01385_FYUU_000_001<tab>Bien qu'il y ait beaucoup de poissons dans les eaux environnantes, des petits en pleine croissanccce ont besoin d'une ali<var 16 /var>men<var 16 /var>ta<var 16 /var>tion variée.

source: TEXT_BANSAH107_01385_FYUU_000_002<tab>Pshhh... If you could head over to Moonshhhade Isle and gather an armful of whitecap clams, it would do much for your ssstanding with the clutch.
target: TEXT_BANSAH107_01385_FYUU_000_002<tab>Fsshhh, les <var 33 ((EventItem)) 0DF61E89750302 /var> de l'îlet d'Ombrelune ssseraient un mets de choix pour mes petits frères. Pourrais-tu m'en rapporter<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_BANSAH107_01385_FYUU_000_003<tab>The clams are a delicacy, you sssee, but we mussst often fight off other predators to claim them. Are you up to the tasssk?
target: TEXT_BANSAH107_01385_FYUU_000_003<tab>Il faut sssouvent combattre d'autres prédateurs pour en obtenir, mais tu es cccer<var 16 /var>tai<var 16 /var>ne<var 16 /var>ment à la hauteur.

source: TEXT_BANSAH107_01385_FYUU_000_004<tab>Pshhh... For this vital errand, I am shhhure Pahh will be glad to offer you the ssservices of his ssswiftest elbssst.
target: TEXT_BANSAH107_01385_FYUU_000_004<tab>Mon frère Pahh te prêtera un elbssst pour aller jusssqu'à l'île.

source: TEXT_BANSAH107_01385_FYUU_000_005<tab>Head over to Moonshhhade Isle, and gather as many whitecap clams as you can find. Jussst be on the lookout for other predators ssseeking to contessst your claim!
target: TEXT_BANSAH107_01385_FYUU_000_005<tab>J'aimerais que tu ailles ramasser cccinq <var 33 ((EventItem)) 0DF61E89750302 /var> sur l'îlet d'Ombrelune. Mais fais attention aux prédateurs qui rôdent là-bas<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_BANSAH107_01385_TAMER01376_000_010<tab>Pshhh... You go to Moonshhhade Isle for clams!? Ah, I can already tassste that sssucculent clam flesh...
target: TEXT_BANSAH107_01385_TAMER01376_000_010<tab>Tu vas chercher des clams à Ombrelune<var 1D /var>? Hmmm, je peux déjà sssentir leur chair juteuse sssur ma langue...

source: TEXT_BANSAH107_01385_Q1_000_000<tab>Ride the elbst to Moonshade Isle?
TEXT_BANSAH107_01385_POPMESSAGE_000_000<tab>An uragnite contests your claim on the clams!
TEXT_BANSAH107_01385_FYUU_000_020<tab>Have you been to Moonshhhade Isle? Let me sssee your haul.
target: TEXT_BANSAH107_01385_FYUU_000_020<tab>Viens-tu me livrer les cccinq <var 33 ((EventItem)) 0DF61E89750302 /var> que je t'ai demandé<var 08 ((<var 28 ((EventItem)) F61E897507 /var>)) ((es)) ((s)) /var><var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_BANSAH107_01385_FYUU_000_025<tab>Pshhh! Thisss is a rare bounty! You have made many friends within the clutch this day.
target: TEXT_BANSAH107_01385_FYUU_000_025<tab>Fsshhh<var 1D /var>! Ils sssont magnifiques<var 1D /var>! Tu vas te faire de nombreux amis iccci avec un présent pareil.

source: TEXT_BANSAH107_01385_FYUU_000_026<tab>I will drop these clams in a rock pool to keep them freshhh. <var 1A 02 /var>Cook<var 1A 01 /var> them? No, no, they mussst be eaten raw, shhhorewalker!
target: TEXT_BANSAH107_01385_FYUU_000_026<tab>Je vais les placccer dans une petite mare d'eau pour les garder au frais. Les <var 1A 02 /var>cuisiner<var 1A 01 /var><var 1D /var>? Non, non, ils doivent être mangés crus, voyons<var 1D /var>! Les sssans-branchies ont des mœurs bien étranges...
